live concert versions of bon jovi 's greatest hits `` one wild night : live 1985-2001 '' by bon jovi , is a compilation of bon jovi 's best songs , performed at various concert events from 1985 to 2001 . for bon jovi fans , it 's classic bob jovi and a must have ! if you like music recorded from `` live '' performances , you will love this album ! if you prefer `` studio-cut '' versions , you may not like this album because it has the sound and feel of a live concert .